     * {
     *   updateElements: {
     *     items: [
     *       {},          // keep item 0
     *       "__DELETE__",  // remove item 1
     *       { value: 5 }, // update item 2
     *       "__DELETE__"   // remove item 3
     *     ]
     *   }
     * }
     * 
     * Complex nested example - updating and deleting within deep structures:
